These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: kiwi, spinach, asparagus, strawberry
Nationality: nigerian, italian, dutch, indonesian
1. Nationality:italian is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
2. Food:kiwi == Nationality:indonesian##1
3. Nationality:dutch is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1
4. Food:spinach is on the left of Nationality:indonesian##1
5. Food:strawberry is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | strawberry | asparagus | spinach | kiwi   |
| Nationality   | italian  | nigerian     | dutch   | indonesian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: card-games, singing, filmmaking, hiking
Sport: handball, ice-hockey, lacrosse, snowboarding
1. Hobby:hiking == Sport:ice-hockey##1
2. Hobby:card-games is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:singing is on the right of Hobby:hiking##1
4. Hobby:hiking is on the right of Sport:lacrosse##1
5. Sport:ice-hockey is on the left of Sport:handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | hiking | singing | card-games    |
| Sport   | lacrosse    | ice-hockey      | handball | snowboarding |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
Hobby: cooking, drawing, gardening, skydiving
Movie-Genre: fantasy, satire, epic, zombie
1. Movie-Genre:epic is on the left of Movie-Genre:zombie##1
2. Hobby:cooking == Movie-Genre:fantasy##1
3. Movie-Genre:satire is on the far right##1
4. Movie-Genre:zombie is on the right of Hobby:skydiving##1
5. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Movie-Genre:satire##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | cooking | skydiving | gardening   | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | epic | zombie | satire         |

